<h1>丧</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">sàng</span><span class=alesi>(sang4)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">sāng</span><span class=alesi>(sang1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 丧 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 丧</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/mourning" style="color:black;">mourning</a>; <a href="/dictionary/mourn" style="color:black;">mourn</a>; <a href="/dictionary/funeral" style="color:black;">funeral</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 8<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 8 strokes: <a href="/character/的" title="de: possessive, adjectival suffix">的</a>, <a href="/character/和" title="he2: harmony, peace; peaceful, calm">和</a>, <a href="/character/国" title="guo2: nation, country, nation-state">国</a>, <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/所" title="suo3: place, location; numerary adjunct">所</a>, <a href="/character/事" title="shi4: affair, matter, business; to serve; accident, incident">事</a>, <a href="/character/经" title="jing1: classic works; pass through">经</a>, <a href="/character/法" title="fa3: law, rule, regulation, statute; France, French">法</a>, <a href="/character/学" title="xue2: learning, knowledge; school">学</a>, <a href="/character/现" title="xian4: appear, manifest, become visible">现</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/十" title="Kangxi radical 24">十</a>&nbsp;24.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 6 <br><small>Other HSK 6 characters: <a href="/character/奴" title="nu2: slave, servant">奴</a>, <a href="/character/渡" title="du4: cross, ferry over; ferry">渡</a>, <a href="/character/旗" title="qi2: banner, flag, streamer">旗</a>, <a href="/character/甘" title="gan1: sweetness; sweet, tasty">甘</a>, <a href="/character/隆" title="long2: prosperous, plentiful, abundant">隆</a>, <a href="/character/扎" title="zha1: pull up; pierce; struggle free">扎</a>, <a href="/character/梁" title="liang2: bridge; beam; rafters; surname">梁</a>, <a href="/character/伏" title="fu2: crouch, crawl, lie hidden, conceal">伏</a>, <a href="/character/皆" title="jie1: all, every, everybody">皆</a>, <a href="/character/晨" title="chen2: early morning, daybreak">晨</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-6" title="List o