h;"></div></div><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">喪|丧[<span style="color:#000099;">sàng</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- to lose sth abstract but important (courage, authority, one's life etc)<br>- to be bereaved of (one's spouse etc)<br>- to die<br>- disappointed<br>- discouraged<br></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div><h2>Details</h2><p><b>Unicode code point:</b> U+4E27</p></div>

